calculator

Class Entry

  • java.lang.Object
    • calculator.Entry

  • public class Entry
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates objects of type number, symbol or string of which can be used to store information as floats i.e "5.0", operation symbols i.e. "+" and string i.e. "5 + 4 - 2".
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0, 10/20/2019
    Author:
    Gilberto Pestana
